import {
    GoogleRecaptchaSection, 
    SectionTitle, 
    SectionForm, 
    FormFieldset, 
    FieldsetLabel,
    FieldsetInput
} from './style';

const Home = () => (
    <GoogleRecaptchaSection>
        <SectionTitle>Google Recaptcha</SectionTitle>

        <SectionForm>
            <FormFieldset className="form__fieldset">
                <FieldsetLabel className="fieldset__label">Type your name:</FieldsetLabel>

                <FieldsetInput title="name" id="name" className="fieldset__name" />
            </FormFieldset>

            <FormFieldset className="form__fieldset">
                <button title="confirm" id="confirm" className="fieldset__button" type="submit">Confirm</button>
            </FormFieldset>
        </SectionForm>
    </GoogleRecaptchaSection>
)

export default Home
